          12,
          16
        ]
      }
    ],
    "roles": [
      {
        "source": "李源祥",
        "target": "Lee Yuen Cheung",
        "role": "Group Chief Executive and President"
      }
    ],
    "terms": [],
    "style_rules": [
      "Use US$ for U.S. dollar amounts.",
      "Keep listed-company annual report disclosure tone formal and publishable.",
      "Do not change numbers, percentages, years, named entities or financial metric values.",
      "Use established financial abbreviations for table labels when provided.",
      "Keep row and column semantics unchanged.",
      "Use n/m for 無意義."
    ]
  },
  "current_unit": {
    "page_no": 15,
    "unit_id": "p15_g02",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 4,
    "source_text": "年度員工敬業度指標調查是我們在各市場共同努力所得成果的重要指標，藉此更瞭解和支援員工。在2020年，\n97%的員工參與調查，本集團所得的員工敬業度評分升至歷來新高，在蓋洛普環球金融服務及保險業基準中排名\n88分位。此外，友邦保險獲列入《福布斯》\n「2020年世界最佳僱主榜單」(‘World’s Best Employers 2020’ list)。",
    "current_translation": "Our annual employee engagement survey is a key indicator of the collective efforts we make across our markets to better understand and support our employees. In 2020, 97% of employees participated in the survey, and our Group achieved a record high employee engagement score, ranking at the 88th percentile against the Gallup Global Financial Services and Insurance benchmark. Additionally, AIA was named on Forbes' 'World's Best Employers 2020' list."
  },
  "output_format": {
    "translations": [
      {
        "unit_id": "p15_g02",
        "translation": "<更紧凑译文>"
      }
    ]
  }
}

